name: Inductive Analog Switch
description: An KiCad library for inductive analog keyboard switches
description_full:
This library contains footprints and symbols for inductive analog keyboard switches for use with the Texas Instruments LDC1312, LDC1314, LDC1312 and LDC1314 inductance to digital converters.
Supported footprints for switches are currently PCB or plate mounted, LED or no LED Cherry MX, Alps Matias or hybrid Cherry MX and Alps Matias.
